        content: "Custom Elements au lifecycle callbacks similare cu React hooks:\n\n```js\nclass MyCounter extends HTMLElement {\n  static observedAttributes = ['start'];\n  \n  constructor() {\n    super();\n    this.count = 0;\n    this.attachShadow({ mode: 'open' });\n  }\n  \n  // Adăugat în DOM\n  connectedCallback() {\n    const start = parseInt(this.getAttribute('start') || '0');\n    this.count = start;\n    this.render();\n  }\n  \n  // Scos din DOM\n  disconnectedCallback() {\n    // cleanup: removeEventListener, clearInterval etc.\n    console.log('Element removed');\n  }\n  \n  // Atribut schimbat\n  attributeChangedCallback(name, oldVal, newVal) {\n    if (name === 'start') {\n      this.count = parseInt(newVal);\n      this.render();\n    }\n  }\n  \n  render() {\n    this.shadowRoot.innerHTML = `\n      <style>button { margin: 0 4px; }</style>\n      <button onclick=\"this.getRootNode().host.decrement()\">-</button>\n      <span>${this.count}</span>\n      <button onclick=\"this.getRootNode().host.increment()\">+</button>\n    `;\n  }\n  \n  increment() { this.count++; this.render(); }\n  decrement() { this.count--; this.render(); }\n}\n\ncustomElements.define('my-counter', MyCounter);\n```\n\n```html\n<my-counter start=\"5\"></my-counter>\n```\n\n**Tabel lifecycle:**\n| Callback | Când e apelat |\n|---|---|\n| constructor() | La creare |\n| connectedCallback() | Adăugat în DOM |\n| disconnectedCallback() | Scos din DOM |\n| attributeChangedCallback() | Atribut din observedAttributes schimbat |\n| adoptedCallback() | Mutat în alt document |"
